cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL 

This paper is about a method to make the structure of neural networks differentiable, which is a topic that falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the use of gradient descent for optimization (cs.LG), and the application of the method to sequence prediction problems (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the potential application of the method to feedforward layered networks (cs.CV) and multiple-area networks (cs.CL).
